		<title>什麼是外匯交易？它是如何運作的？</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/trading-strategies/what-is-forex-trading-how-does-it-work</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 04:12:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[交易策略]]></category>
